# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002500> (causal agent in process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002500> "A relationship between a material entity and a process where the material entity has some causal role that influences the process")
